===多樣性===
現存的棘皮動物約有7000種，已滅絕的約有13000種。<ref name=Tree />棲息地從潮間帶淺灘到深海都有。棘皮動物大致可分為兩類。一類較為擅長[[移動性_(生物體)|運動]]，包括[[海星|海星]]（1745種）、[[蛇尾|蛇尾]]（2300種）、[[海膽|海膽]]（900種）和[[海參|海參]]（1430種）；另一類則包括[[海百合|海百合]]（580種）以及已滅絕的[[海蕾亞門|海蕾亞門]]和[[擬海百合|擬海百合]]。<ref name="Uthicke">{{cite journal |last1=Uthicke |first1=Sven |author2=Schaffelke, Britta |author3=Byrne, Maria |date=1 January 2009 |title=A boom–bust phylum? Ecological and evolutionary consequences of density variations in echinoderms |journal=Ecological Monographs |volume=79 |pages=3–24 |doi=10.1890/07-2136.1 |doi-access=free }}</ref>

[[File:fossile-seelilie.jpg|thumb]]
[[File:Hyperoblastus.jpg|thumb]]時期的[[海蕾|海蕾]]，''[[Hyperoblastus|Hyperoblastus]]''，於[[威斯康辛州|威斯康辛州]]發現]]

所有棘皮動物都是[[海洋生物|海洋生物]]，其中絕大多數屬於[[海底生物界|海底生物界]]。<ref name="Waggoner">{{cite web |last=Waggoner |first=Ben |url=http://www.ucmp.berkeley.edu/echinodermata/echinofr.html |title=Echinodermata: Fossil Record |date=16 January 1995 |work=Introduction to the Echinodermata |publisher=Museum of Paleontology: University of California at Berkeley |access-date=14 March 2013 |archive-date=2015-05-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150512092459/http://www.ucmp.berkeley.edu/echinodermata/echinofr.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

===化石歷史===
已知的最古老的棘皮動物[[化石|化石]]可能是來自澳大利亞[[前寒武紀|前寒武紀]]的''{{le|Arkarua}}''。該物種呈圓盤狀，邊緣有放射狀的脊，中央有一個五角形的凹陷，上面有放射狀的線。然而，沒有證據顯示''Arkarua''體內具有水管系統，因此''Arkarua''不一定屬於棘皮動物。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ucmp.berkeley.edu/vendian/arkarua.html |title=Vendian Animals: ''Arkarua'' |last=Smith |first=Dave |date=28 September 2005 |access-date=2013-03-14 |archive-date=2021-07-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210709183045/https://ucmp.berkeley.edu/vendian/arkarua.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

一般意義上的棘皮動物出現在寒武紀，出現於[[奧陶紀|奧陶紀]]的海星亞門與海百合是[[古生代|古生代]]的主要類群。<ref name=Waggoner/>棘皮動物留下了大量的化石記錄。<ref name=Waggoner/>據推測，棘皮動物的祖先是一種結構簡單的兩側對稱動物，有嘴、消化道和肛門，營附著生活，是濾食性動物。棘皮動物的幼蟲都是兩側對稱的，經變態發育成為輻射對稱。成年的海星和海百合仍然會附著在海床上。{{sfn|Dorit|Walker|Barnes|1991|pp=792–793}}

古生代棘皮動物呈球狀，附著於[[基質_(生物生活環境)|基質]]上，口面朝上。隨著演化，除海百合外的所有棘皮動物均變為口面向下，其管足也失去了進食功能，轉而承擔起運動功能。部分棘皮動物漸漸放棄附著生活，並發展出具有{{link-en|井骨|Stereom}}的內骨骼盤和用於進食的外睫狀溝。<ref>{{cite web |author=UCMP Berkeley |title=Echinodermata: Morphology |url=http://www.ucmp.berkeley.edu/echinodermata/echinomm.html |work=University of California Museum of Paleontology |access-date=21 March 2011 |archive-date=2016-06-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160624102524/http://www.ucmp.berkeley.edu/echinodermata/echinomm.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>棘皮動物化石的{{link-en|步帶溝|Ambulacral}}向下延伸到身體的一側，兩側有腕，結構與現代海百合的羽枝十分類似。{{sfn|Dorit|Walker|Barnes|1991|pp=792–793}}

==解剖與生理==
棘皮動物由兩側對稱的動物進化而來。成年的[[現生種|現生種]]棘皮動物大多呈五輻射對稱，而棘皮動物幼蟲則具有[[纖毛|纖毛]]，可自由移動，看起來像胚胎期的脊索動物。隨著發育，棘皮動物的右側肢體漸漸退化消失，而左側肢體則發育為五輻射對稱狀。{{sfn|Ruppert|Fox|Barnes|2004|p=873}}不過也有部分棘皮動物不是五輻射對稱。如：[[項鏈海星目|項鏈海星目]]中也有部分六腕海星，此外某些蛇尾也是六腕的，例如[[錦疣蛇尾|錦疣蛇尾]]（''Ophiothala danae''）、{{link-en|輻蛇尾|Ophiactis savignyi}}等。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://books.google.no/books?id=EtkqDwAAQBAJ&pg=PA323&dq=Seven+Ophiacantha+species+are+recorded+from+the&hl=no&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwiK5Laq98zYAhUjhqYKHVBzBL4Q6AEIKDAA#v=onepage&q=Seven%20Ophiacantha%20species%20are%20recorded%20from%20the&f=false |title=Australian Echinoderms: Biology, Ecology and Evolution |access-date=2021-08-24 |archive-date=2021-07-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210709182929/https://books.google.no/books?id=EtkqDwAAQBAJ&pg=PA323&dq=Seven+Ophiacantha+species+are+recorded+from+the&hl=no&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwiK5Laq98zYAhUjhqYKHVBzBL4Q6AEIKDAA#v=onepage&q=Seven%20Ophiacantha%20species%20are%20recorded%20from%20the&f=false |dead-url=no }}</ref>

某些棘皮動物的腕數是五的倍數，如{{link-en|南極太陽海星|Labidiaster annulatus}}擁有50腕，而{{link-en|許氏大羽花|Comaster schlegelii}}則有200腕。<ref name="Messing">{{cite web |url=http://www.nova.edu/ocean/messing/crinoids/4%20Morphology%20crown%20&%20calyx.html |title=Crown and calyx |last=Messing |first=Charles |work=Charles Messing's Crinoid Pages |access-date=29 July 2012 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131029193832/http://www.nova.edu/ocean/messing/crinoids/4%20Morphology%20crown%20%26%20calyx.html |archive-date=29 October 2013 |url-status=dead }}</ref>

==再生==
[[File:Sea_star_regenerating_legs.jpg|thumb]]

棘皮動物的[[再生|再生]]能力很強。許多棘皮動物為了逃生會[[自割|自動斷腕或排出內臟]]，而這些器官之後又會再生。例如海膽的刺、海星和海百合的腕，以及海參的內臟。海參在感到威脅時會排出部分內臟，這些內臟要經過幾個月才能再生，在這段時間內，海參會以儲存的營養物質為生，並從水中吸收溶解的有機物。<ref name="dobson1991">{{cite journal |doi=10.2307/1542439 |pmid=29303627 |volume=180 |issue=1 |pages=167–184 |last=Dobson |first=W. E. |author2=S. E. Stancyk |author3=L. A. Clements |author4=R. M. Showman |title=Nutrient Translocation during Early Disc Regeneration in the Brittlestar ''Microphiopholis gracillima'' (Stimpson) (Echinodermata: Ophiuroidea) |journal=Biol Bull |access-date=2011-07-14 |date=1 February 1991 |jstor=1542439 |url=http://www.biolbull.org/cgi/reprint/180/1/167 |archive-date=2008-09-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080904224148/http://www.biolbull.org/cgi/reprint/180/1/167 |dead-url=no }}</ref>一般來說，海星的斷腕如果不包含與身體相連的部分就難以長成新的海星，但某些棘皮動物可以僅靠斷腕再生，一些棘皮動物甚至將此作為[[無性繁殖|無性繁殖]]的方式。<ref name="Edmondson1935">{{cite journal |last=Edmondson |first=C.H |title=Autotomy and regeneration of Hawaiian starfishes |journal=Bishop Museum Occasional Papers |year=1935 |volume=11 |issue=8 |pages=3–20 |url=http://hbs.bishopmuseum.org/pubs-online/pdf/op11-8.pdf |access-date=2021-08-25 |archive-date=2012-10-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121003203440/http://hbs.bishopmuseum.org/pubs-online/pdf/op11-8.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="McAlaray1987">{{Cite conference |publisher=National Park Service |conference=3rd California Islands Symposium |last=McAlary |first=Florence A |title=Population Structure and Reproduction of the Fissiparous Seastar, ''Linckia columbiae'' Gray, on Santa Catalina Island, California |access-date=2012-04-15 |year=1993 |url=http://repository.library.csuci.edu/handle/10139/3393 |archive-date=2012-07-22 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/69M5u7CP6?url=http://repository.library.csuci.edu/handle/10139/3393 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Hotchkiss2000">See last paragraph in review above Analysis{{cite journal |doi=10.1093/icb/40.3.340 |volume=40 |issue=3 |pages=340–354 |last=Hotchkiss |first=Frederick H. C. |title=On the Number of Rays in Starfish |journal=American Zoologist |date=1 June 2000 |doi-access=free}}</ref><ref name="Fisher1925">{{Cite journal |doi=10.2307/1536659 |issn=0006-3185 |volume=48 |issue=3 |pages=171–175 |last=Fisher |first=W. K. |title=Asexual Reproduction in the Starfish, ''Sclerasterias'' |journal=Biological Bulletin |access-date=2011-07-15 |date=1 March 1925 |jstor=1536659 |url=http://www.biolbull.org/cgi/reprint/48/3/171.pdf |archive-date=2010-03-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100331164738/http://www.biolbull.org/cgi/reprint/48/3/171.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>

棘皮動物的再生形式包括{{link-en|新建再生|epimorphosis}}和{{link-en|變形再生|morphallaxis}}。在新建再生的過程中，幹細胞形成{{link-en|芽體|Blastema}}並生成新組織。變形再生則包括移動和重塑現有組織以取代丟失的部分。有時某些組織會直接[[分化轉移|分化轉移]]成另一種組織。<ref name="Mashanov2005">{{cite journal |doi=10.2307/3593108 |volume=209 |issue=3 |pages=184–193 |last=Mashanov |first=Vladimir S. |author2=Igor Yu. Dolmatov |author3=Thomas Heinzeller |title=Transdifferentiation in Holothurian Gut Regeneration |journal=Biol Bull |access-date=2011-07-15 |date=1 December 2005 |jstor=3593108 |url=http://www.biolbull.org/cgi/reprint/209/3/184 |pmid=16382166 |s2cid=27847466 |archive-date=2008-07-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080724061021/http://www.biolbull.org/cgi/reprint/209/3/184 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

棘皮動物幼蟲在生長過程中不易受外界影響，這使得棘皮動物被廣泛用作[[發育生物學|發育生物學]]的[[模式生物|模式生物]]。<ref>{{cite journal |last=Hart |first=M. W. |date=Jan–Feb 2002 |title=Life history evolution and comparative developmental biology of echinoderms |journal= Evolution and Development|volume=4 |issue=1 |pages=62–71 |pmid=11868659 |doi=10.1046/j.1525-142x.2002.01052.x |s2cid=39175905 }}</ref>

==分佈和棲息地==
棘皮動物（尤其是海星和海參）的幼蟲能在洋流的幫助下到遠洋帶生活，這使得棘皮動物的分佈十分廣泛。<ref>{{cite encyclopedia |url=http://www.britannica.com/EBchecked/topic/177910/echinoderm/25727/Distribution-and-abundance |author=Pawson, David Leo |title=Echinoderm: distribution and abundance |encyclopedia=Encyclopædia Britannica |access-date=2013-06-28 |archive-date=2014-09-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140913063136/http://www.britannica.com/EBchecked/topic/177910/echinoderm/25727/Distribution-and-abundance/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>它們幾乎可以在所有深度和緯度的海洋中找到，有時一片海域90%的生物都是棘皮動物。棘皮動物在珊瑚礁附近的多樣性是最高的，而淺灘上也有它們的身影。此外，海百合在極地最為豐富，而作為底棲和穴居生物的海參則在深海中十分常見。幾乎所有棘皮動物都是底棲動物，但有些海百合是{{link-en|假浮游生物|Pseudoplankton}}，它們會附著在漂浮的圓木和碎片上。這種行為在古生代最為常見，當時還沒有藤壺等生物與其競爭。<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Xiaofeng |first1=Wang |last2=Hagdorn |first2=Hans |last3=Chuanshang |first3=Wang |date=September 2006 |title=Pseudoplanktonic lifestyle of the Triassic crinoid ''Traumatocrinus'' from Southwest China |journal=[[Lethaia|Lethaia]] |volume=39 |issue=3 |pages=187–193 |doi=10.1080/00241160600715321 }}</ref>

==生態==
棘皮動物是一類數量眾多，體型較大的無脊椎動物，在海洋、底棲[[生態系統|生態系統]]中發揮著重要作用。<ref name=Uthicke/>[[沙錢|沙錢]]、海參和某些海星在挖掘巢穴的過程中攪起海底沉積物，使氧氣得以滲入海底更深層，有助於微生物消耗海底的營養物質，建立更複雜的生態系統。海膽、海星和蛇尾可以阻止珊瑚礁上的藻蓆生長，給濾食性生物提供生存條件，提高珊瑚礁的生物多樣性。<ref name=Miller>{{cite encyclopedia |url=http://www.britannica.com/EBchecked/topic/177910/echinoderm |last=Miller |first=John E. |title=Echinoderm: role in nature |encyclopedia=Encyclopædia Britannica |access-date=2013-06-28 |archive-date=2015-04-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150430073216/http://www.britannica.com/EBchecked/topic/177910/echinoderm |dead-url=no }}</ref>某些海膽會鑽入堅硬的岩石，使其中的營養物質得到釋放。珊瑚礁亦會被海膽破壞，但其生長速度通常大於海膽的侵蝕速度。<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Herrera-Escalante |first1=T. |last2=López-Pérez |first2=R. A. |last3=Leyte-Morales |first3=G. E. |year=2005 |title=Bioerosion caused by the sea urchin ''Diadema mexicanum'' (Echinodermata: Echinoidea) at Bahías de Huatulco, Western Mexico. |journal=Revista de Biología Tropical |volume=53 |issue=3 |pages=263–273 |pmid=17469255 }}</ref>據估計，棘皮動物每年以[[碳酸鈣|碳酸鈣]]的形式儲存約1億噸碳，為全球[[碳循環|碳循環]]做出了重要貢獻。<ref name="Lebrato Iglesias-Rodríguez 2010">{{cite journal |last1=Lebrato |first1=Mario |last2=Iglesias-Rodríguez |first2=Debora |last3=Feely |first3=Richard A. |last4=Greeley |first4=Dana |last5=Jones |first5=Daniel O. B. |last6=Suarez-Bosche |first6=Nadia |last7=Lampitt |first7=Richard S. |last8=Cartes |first8=Joan E. |last9=Green |first9=Darryl R. H. |last10=Alker |first10=Belinda |title=Global contribution of echinoderms to the marine carbon cycle: CaCO3 budget and benthic compartments |journal=Ecological Monographs |volume=80 |issue=3 |year=2010 |pages=441–467 |issn=0012-9615 |doi=10.1890/09-0553.1|doi-access=free }}</ref>

棘皮動物的數量有時會大幅波動，進而影響生態系統的穩定性。例如，1983年加勒比地區的{{link-en|石灰海膽|Diadema antillarum}}大量死亡，導致珊瑚礁系統被藻類破壞。<ref>{{cite book |last=Osborne |first=Patrick L. |title=Tropical Ecosystem and Ecological Concepts |url=https://archive.org/details/tropicalecosyste0000osbo |year=2000 |publisher=Cambridge University Press |location=Cambridge |isbn=0-521-64523-9 |pages=[https://archive.org/details/tropicalecosyste0000osbo/page/464 464] }}</ref>海膽是珊瑚礁上的主要食草動物之一，它們與藻類之間通常保持著平衡。但捕食者（如：水獺、海螯蝦和魚類）的減少會導致海膽增加，從而殃及[[海藻林|海藻林]]。<ref>{{cite journal |last=Lawrence |first=J. M. |year=1975 |title=On the relationships between marine plants and sea urchins |journal=Oceanographic Marine Biological Annual Review |volume=13 |pages=213–286 |url=http://biology.usf.edu/faculty/data/relationships.pdf |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110205235225/http://biology.usf.edu/faculty/data/relationships.pdf |archive-date=5 February 2011}}</ref>在大堡礁，以活珊瑚為食的[[棘冠海星|棘冠海星]]數量一度驟增，對當地珊瑚礁的[[生物多樣性|生物多樣性]]產生了相當大的影響。目前還不清楚棘冠海星為何會突然增加。<ref>{{cite book |last1=Birkeland |first1=Charles |last2=Lucas |first2=John S. |title=''Acanthaster planci'': Major Management Problem of Coral Reefs |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=Z57rozbkLTAC |year=1990 |publisher=CRC Press |location=Florida |isbn=0849365996 |access-date=2021-08-28 |archive-date=2021-08-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210828055054/https://books.google.com/books?id=Z57rozbkLTAC |dead-url=no }}</ref>

許多生物都以棘皮動物為食，如[[硬骨魚|硬骨魚]]、[[鯊魚|鯊魚]]、{{link-en|絨鴨|Eider}}、[[海鷗|海鷗]]、[[螃蟹|螃蟹]]、[[腹足綱|腹足類動物]]、[[海獺|海獺]]、[[北極狐|北極狐]]和人類。某些較大的海星會以較小的海星為食，而海星大量的卵和幼蟲也為許多海洋生物所食。相較之下海百合的天敵並不多。<ref name=Miller/>某些寄生或共生生物會棲息於海參或海星的體腔內，包括部分魚、蟹、蠕蟲和蝸牛。<ref>{{cite journal |url=https://www.academia.edu/1039201 |title=The symbiotic relationship between Sea cucumbers (Holothuriidae) and Pearlfish (Carapidae) |last1=Luciano |first1=Brooke |last2=Lyman |first2=Ashleigh |last3=McMillan |first3=Selena |last4=Nickels |first4=Abby |journal=Bio.classes.ucsc.edu |access-date=27 June 2013 |archive-date=2021-08-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210828055053/https://www.academia.edu/1039201 |dead-url=no }}</ref>{{better source needed|date=February 2021}}

==用途==
===食用和藥用===
[[File:Sea_urchin_eggs.jpg|thumb]]
[[File:Yokohama_Chinese_Medicine_Sea_cucumber_2.jpg|thumb]]的海參]]

2010年，中國捕獲了37.3萬噸棘皮動物，包括15.8萬噸海參和7.3萬噸海膽，主要用作食物與中藥。<ref name="PangestutiArifin2018">{{cite journal |last1=Pangestuti |first1=Ratih |last2=Arifin |first2=Zainal |title=Medicinal and health benefit effects of functional sea cucumbers |journal=Journal of Traditional and Complementary Medicine |volume=8 |issue=3|year=2018 |pages=341–351 |issn=2225-4110 |doi=10.1016/j.jtcme.2017.06.007|pmid=29992105 |pmc=6035309 |doi-access=free }}</ref><ref>Sourced from the data reported in the [[FAO|FAO]] [http://faostat.fao.org/site/629/default.aspx FishStat database] {{Wayback|url=http://faostat.fao.org/site/629/default.aspx |date=20121107001620 }}</ref>東南亞的一些國家也有食用海參的習慣，一些海參面臨著被過度捕撈的危險。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://dotearth.blogs.nytimes.com/2009/04/01/sea-cucumbers-threatened-by-asian-trade/?_php=true&_type=blogs&_r=0 |title=Sea Cucumbers Threatened by Asian Trade |work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]] |date=April 2009 |access-date=2009-04-01 |archive-date=2020-08-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200804162846/https://dotearth.blogs.nytimes.com/2009/04/01/sea-cucumbers-threatened-by-asian-trade/?_php=true&_type=blogs&_r=0 |dead-url=no }}</ref>常見的海參品種有[[梅花參|梅花參]]和[[紅腹海參|紅腹海參]]。烹飪海參的方法通常是先煮20分鐘，然後自然晾乾，再用火熏烤。海膽的雄性和雌性生殖腺也可食用，特別是[[日本|日本]]、[[秘魯|秘魯]]、[[西班牙|西班牙]]和[[法國|法國]]等國尤其愛吃海膽。海膽口感嫩滑，入口即化，嘗起來就像海鮮和水果的混合物。<ref>{{cite book |last=Lawrence |first=John M. |year=2001 |chapter=The edible sea urchins |volume=37 |pages=1–4 |title=Edible Sea Urchins: Biology and Ecology |editor=John M. Lawrence |doi=10.1016/S0167-9309(01)80002-8 |series=Developments in Aquaculture and Fisheries Science |isbn=9780444503909}}</ref>為防止海膽被[[過度捕撈|過度捕撈]]，目前已開展了一些海膽養殖試驗。<ref>{{cite journal |title=Echinoculture: the rearing of Paracentrotus lividus in a recirculating aquaculture system—experiments of artificial diets for the maintenance of sexual maturation |journal=Aquaculture International |date=February 2015 |last=Sartori D. |first=Scuderi A. |author2=Sansone G. |author3=Gaion A. |doi=10.1007/s10499-014-9802-6 |volume=23 |pages=111–125 |s2cid=18856183}}</ref>

===科研用途===
海膽亦可用於科研，特別是作為發育生物學和生態毒理學的模式生物。<ref name="Insight from the Sea Urchin">{{cite web |url=http://www.exploratorium.edu/imaging-station/research/urchin/story_urchin1.php |title=Insight from the Sea Urchin |work=Microscope Imaging Station |publisher=Exploratorium |access-date=2013-02-04 |archive-date=2017-03-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170312223637/https://www.exploratorium.edu/imaging-station/research/urchin/story_urchin1.php |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |title=Toxicity of polyunsaturated aldehydes of diatoms to Indo-Pacific bioindicator organism Echinometra mathaei |journal=Drug and Chemical Toxicology |date=2015 |last=Sartori D. |first=Gaion A. |doi=10.3109/01480545.2015.1041602 |pmid=25945412 |pages=124–8 |volume=39 |issue=2 |s2cid=207437380 }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|title =Arsenic Exposure Affects Embryo Development of Sea Urchin, Paracentrotus lividus (Lamarck, 1816) |journal=Bulletin of Environmental Contamination and Toxicology|date =2013 |last= Gaion A. |first=Scuderi A. |author2= Pellegrini D. |author3= Sartori D. |doi=10.3109/01480545.2015.1041602 |pages=124–8 |pmid=25945412 |volume=39 |issue=2|s2cid=207437380}}</ref>{{link-en|紫球海膽|Strongylocentrotus purpuratus}}和{{link-en|大西洋紫海膽|Arbacia punctulata}}則可用於胚胎學研究。<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Longo |first1=F. J. |last2=Anderson |first2=E. |date=June 1969 |title=Sperm differentiation in the sea urchins ''Arbacia punctulata'' and ''Strongylocentrotus purpuratus'' |journal=Journal of Ultrastructure Research |volume=27 |issue=5 |pages=486–509 |pmid=5816822 |doi=10.1016/S0022-5320(69)80046-8 }}</ref>海膽卵體積大，透明度高，便於觀察[[受精|受精]]。<ref name="Insight from the Sea Urchin"/>而研究蛇尾腕的再生則有助於治療[[神經退化障礙|神經退化障礙]]。<ref name=Barkhouse/>

===其他用途===
在缺乏[[石灰岩|石灰岩]]的地區，農民將棘皮動物的骨骼作為石灰的來源，有些用於製造魚粉。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.wildsingapore.com/wildfacts/echinodermata/asteroidea/asteroidea.htm |title=Sea stars |publisher=Wild Singapore |access-date=2013-02-04 |archive-date=2021-11-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211113202625/http://www.wildsingapore.com/wildfacts/echinodermata/asteroidea/asteroidea.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>每年有4000噸棘皮動物用於上述用途。這類型的貿易通常由[[貝類|貝類]][[養殖|養殖]]戶，原因是他們會以[[魚|魚]]當食物來源。此外，[[海星|海星]]還可用作製造動物飼料、手工藝品、[[堆肥|堆肥]]和乾燥的標本。<ref name="Barkhouse">{{cite journal |last1=Barkhouse |first1=C. |last2=Niles |first2=M. |last3=Davidson |first3=L. A. |year=2007 |title=A literature review of sea star control methods for bottom and off bottom shellfish cultures |journal=Canadian Industry Report of Fisheries and Aquatic Sciences |volume=279 |issue=7 |pages=14–15 |issn=1488-5409 |url=http://www.dfo-mpo.gc.ca/Library/330342.pdf |access-date=2021-08-26 |archive-date=2013-05-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130522142114/http://www.dfo-mpo.gc.ca/Library/330342.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>

